Caitlin EJ Meyer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Caitlin_EJ_Meyer 0 Caitlin Elizabeth Joelle Meyer (born February 29, 1992) is an American actress. She has appeared in Little Secrets among other roles. Her first stage role was as The Little Match Girl and her first film role was in the 2002 film I Saw Mommy Kissing Santa Claus. She has five brothers and two sisters. Her mother was born and raised in England and her father was raised in Washington D.C.. She has won two Young Artist Awards for her performances.
